% An additional script created by MathWorks specifically for MATLAB Online users 
% is included with each exercise. These companion scripts are designed to be used 
% after completing the programming exercise. They will show you how to use the 
% latest MATLAB machine learning functions and apps used by researchers and professionals 
% to perform the tasks in the programming exercise. You'll also be introduced 
% to the latest tools, features, and datatypes essential to data analysis in MATLAB 
% that weren't available when _Machine Learning_ was created.
